## ⚡ Electricity – San José Clean Energy
**Description:** San José Clean Energy (SJCE) is San José’s local, not-for-profit electricity supplier operated by the City of San José Energy Department. It provides clean energy for residents and businesses at competitive rates, while offering community programs, local control, and more transparency and accessibility.

